metadata.name: Floating Downtown
metadata.description:
Edition: 1/1
Attached file: 2649 x 3311 pixels 

Story: A rare morning in Dubai. Conditions that only form a few times a year. The city covered in a sea of clouds with the dramatic skyscrapers protruding through. These are the mornings photographers dream of. Mornings that are very close to my heart. This marked the start of a new part of my life. I had just relocated to Dubai. I heard there was possibility of the famous fog to make an appearance at sunrise. Setting multiple alarms, I woke up at 4am to no visibility outside my apartment. But this only meant one thing. The fog was here. 

The only way to achieve what I wanted would be with a drone. I flew up into the clouds. Watching the drone disappear into the fog. After a few long seconds the drone broke through to the other side. Revealing an incredible sight. A floating city, above the clouds. This was an incredible way to start my new life in Dubai. A sunrise mission I will always remember.
